{
  "id": "adv_love_2311_08_02",
  "title": "Episode 8 Part 2",
  "script": [
    {
      "type": "bgm",
      "action": "play",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_main-01.m4a",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "background",
      "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBackground/env_adv_2d_outsidehall-00-noon.webp",
      "bgName": "outsidehall-00-noon",
      "startTime": 0
    },
    {
      "type": "choice_selection",
      "choices": [
        {
          "text": "関係を続ける",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh004.m4a",
              "text": "俺はこれからも一緒にいたい",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I want to stay together from now on.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 53.7666663487,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_flashback-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 56.2333353042
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs004.m4a",
              "text": "……ふふ、そっか\nなんだか前もこんなことあったよね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…Hehe‚ I see. I feel like\nwe've had this conversation before.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 56.2333353042,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh005.m4a",
              "text": "高三になった頃のことか？\n……確かに、あの時の状況と\n結構似てるかもしれないな",
              "translations": {
                "en": "You mean when we were\nthe 3rd-year of high school?\n…Now that you mention it‚\nthe situation is pretty similar.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 62.600000445,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs005.m4a",
              "text": "あの時はまだまだ子供だったけど\n私達、そろそろ真剣に将来を考えなきゃ\nいけないくらい大人になったよね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "We were still kids back then‚\nbut now we become adults‚\nwho should start to think about\nthe future seriously.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 69.7000014622,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs006.m4a",
              "text": "三年半、あっという間だったな～\n本当に楽しかった。でも……正直に言うね\n私達、今が別れ時じゃない？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "3 years and a half passed so fast~.\nI really had fun‚ but…\nI'll be straight. Don't you think\nit's time for us to break up?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 79.033338356,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 95.833342425
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh006.m4a",
              "text": "本当に正直だな\n確かに、今の俺達はお世辞にも\nうまくいってるとは言えないと思う",
              "translations": {
                "en": "That's really straight.\nYou're right‚ I don't think\nwe can say things are going well\nbetween us right now.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 96.7000009536,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_contact-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 103.9666645685
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh007.m4a",
              "text": "だけど……何か決定的なことがあった\n訳でもない。そうだろ？",
              "translations": {
                "en": "But… nothing decisive has happened‚\nright?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 103.9666645685,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs007.m4a",
              "text": "そう……だね\n「なんだかうまくいかないな」って\nいうのが少しずつ重なってきた感じ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "That's… true. The feeling of\n\"things aren't going well\"\nhas been slowly building up.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 109.89999485,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh008.m4a",
              "text": "それなら……これからいくらでも\nどうにか出来るって。俺は……宣言通り\n渚を支える編集者を目指すから",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Then… we can still work things out.\nI'll… become an editor\nwho supports you‚ Nagisa‚\njust like I said.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 117.9666660943,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs008.m4a",
              "text": "……そっか。うん、分かった\n{user}くんのその言葉……\n信じてみるね",
              "translations": {
                "en": "…I see. Okay‚ I understand.\nI'll trust you‚ {user}-kun.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 127.3333302178,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 130.7333394049
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_tension-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 136.0666777925
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh009.m4a",
              "text": "（だが――現実はそう甘くはなかった）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（But――reality wasn't that easy.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 136.0666777925,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh010.m4a",
              "text": "（渚がデビューした出版社に、俺も無事採用\nされたが、出版不況を受け大幅に経営が悪化\nその煽りを受け、唐突に左遷される羽目に）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（I successfully joined the publisher\nwhere Nagisa debuted‚ but due to\nthe financial strain by recession‚\nI was suddenly transferred.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 140.0333627697,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh011.m4a",
              "text": "（渚の担当編集をするどころか\n一転して……遠距離恋愛をすることに\nなってしまった）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（Far from becoming Nagisa's editor‚\nI ended up… in a long-distance\nrelationship.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 152.3667093273,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 159.2000426606
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": null,
              "speakerName": "",
              "speakerNameEn": "",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": null,
              "text": "―― 一人暮らしを始めてしばらく経った頃",
              "translations": {
                "en": "――Some time after I started\nliving alone",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 160.0667095816,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_gasa-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 3066.6643777999807
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-03.m4a",
                  "delay": 5233.311716799989
                },
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 14533.3117168
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_pretty-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 161.9000406261
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh012.m4a",
              "text": "ん？　渚から郵便物……これは新作小説だな\n遠く離れた二人の恋物語……？\n読んでみるかな",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Hmm? A package from Nagisa…\nthis is her new novel. \"A love story\nof a couple who are far apart\"…?\nI should read it.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 162.7667072928,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 175.4667248403
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_book-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 176.9667032239
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh013.m4a",
              "text": "（最後のページをめくるとそこには\n一枚のメモが挟まっていた）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（When I turned to the last page‚\nthere was a note tucked inside.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 177.6667154307,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_letter-01.m4a",
                  "delay": 4766.621463099995
                }
              ]
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "Nagisa Ibuki",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa Ibuki",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs009.m4a",
              "text": "『大丈夫』",
              "translations": {
                "en": "\"Don't worry\"",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 183.8666920338,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_heart-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 185.1504622851
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh014.m4a",
              "text": "ありがとう、渚。俺も……諦めないで\nまたそばにいられるように頑張ってみるよ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Thank you‚ Nagisa. I won't give up.\nI'll try my best…\nso we can be together again.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 185.9667042408,
              "sfxList": []
            }
          ]
        },
        {
          "text": "関係を終わらせる",
          "route": [
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_sad-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 195.6333709074
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh015.m4a",
              "text": "そろそろ……終わりにしようか\n別れよう、俺達",
              "translations": {
                "en": "It's time… for us to end this.\nLet's break up‚ Nagisa.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 195.6333709074,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs010.m4a",
              "text": "うん……そうだよね\nそれが……いい、よね……っ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Yeah… you're right.\nThat'll be… good for us‚ right…?",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 202.6000406258,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh016.m4a",
              "text": "本当は、これからも渚のそばにいたい\nだけど……このままじゃ、お互いに\n疲れてしまうと思う",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I always want to be with you.\nHowever… if we continue this‚\nwe'll both just end up exhausted.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 209.6333709073,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh017.m4a",
              "text": "だから、もう元の関係に……友達に戻ろう",
              "translations": {
                "en": "So‚ let's go back to\nhow we were before…\nLet's be friends again.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 219.2000426602,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs011.m4a",
              "text": "うん……うん……\n今までありがとう……",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Okay… ok…\nThank you for everything…",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 226.1667042406,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh018.m4a",
              "text": "（それから俺は、出版とは関係無い業界に\n就職した。大学の卒業式の日……\n渚は、寂しげな笑みを浮かべていた）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（After that‚ I got a job\nunrelated to publishing.\nOn the graduation day…\nNagisa was wearing a sad smile.）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 232.7333597174,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "unknown",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": null,
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh019.m4a",
              "text": "（渚のことを引きずりながらも……\n慌ただしい生活の中で、少しずつ傷が\n癒されていた、ある日のこと）",
              "translations": {
                "en": "（While I hadn't gotten over her…\nthe hustle and bustle of daily life\nslowly healed my wounds.\nThen‚ one day…）",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 244.5333556484,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "stop",
              "startTime": 252.9666889818
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_cafe-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 254.2666889818
            },
            {
              "type": "bgm",
              "action": "play",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_bgm_adv_stm-01.m4a",
              "startTime": 254.2666889818
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "koh",
              "speakerName": "{user}",
              "speakerNameEn": "{user}",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-kohei.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-koh020.m4a",
              "text": "渚からご飯に誘ってくるとはな……\n会うのはかなり久しぶりだ",
              "translations": {
                "en": "I didn't expect Nagisa invited me\nto dinner… It's been a long time\nsince we last saw each other.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 255.0666889818,
              "sfxList": []
            },
            {
              "type": "sfx",
              "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
              "startTime": 260.4666961029
            },
            {
              "type": "dialogue",
              "speakerCode": "ngs",
              "speakerName": "伊吹渚",
              "speakerNameEn": "Nagisa",
              "iconUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/iconCharacter/chara-nagisa.png",
              "voiceUrl": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/loveStoryVoice/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02/sud_vo_adv_love_2311_08_02-ngs012.m4a",
              "text": "久しぶり",
              "translations": {
                "en": "Long time no see.",
                "id": ""
              },
              "startTime": 262.1000548672,
              "sfxList": [
                {
                  "src": "https://apiip.dasewasia.my.id/storyBgm/sud_se_adv_walk-in-single-02.m4a",
